markets.title: Will Multiple teams win the Hyperliquid validator vote for the USDH ticker?
markets.rules_primary: If Multiple teams is selected through the Hyperliquid validator vote to receive the USDH ticker designation before Jan 1, 2026, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: Resolution is based on which team receives the most stake-weighted validator votes during the official voting period. If Hyperliquid Foundation validators abstain and align with the non-Foundation majority, their stake counts toward the team with the most non-Foundation support. If no team receives votes or the vote is cancelled, all markets resolve to No unless "None/No team selected" is listed. Ties resolve to No unless Hyperliquid implements an official tiebreaker. Only the initial official announcement determines resolution; subsequent disputes or reversals after expiration do not affect the outcome.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the validator vote concludes and a winner is announced.
